title: Julia's Tabata Workout Part 5 - Week 3 Set 1 Intermediate/Advanced: Best for Toning and Fat Loss

sources.title: Shocker Internet Drive In Week 5 - Driller Killer (70's Drive In Fun)
sources.description: It's that time again kids! Grab your girl and load a few friends up into the trunk of your Chevy because we are going back to the Shocker Internet Drive In. This week we proudly present that low budget 1979 slasher/psycho classic - "Driller Killer". Of course we have included another Bugs Bunny cartoon as well as some "snack bar" teasers to get your taste buds going. So drive on in, but we do reserve the right to check the trunk of your car for stowaways looking to skip buying a ticket. But, of course, our drive in is free so don't sweat the little stuff. Grab a soda, a little popcorn, snuggle up with your favorite girl (or guy) and enjoy the show! NEW Facebook Address:  https://www.facebook.com/shockerdrivein.dx.am website: http://shockerdrivein.dx.am or http://shockerdrivein.freeoda.com

metadata.Plot: Get the benefit of a cardiovascular workout in a short amount of time and continue burning fat for the next 24-48 hours with this intense Tabata style HIIT routine.
